O lovely dear sainted boxes. He got the stopwatch and went on with the story, ending his segment with Careless up to his hips in a pool of quicksand or something, and then he would ask someone else if he or she could, and bang down the button on the stopwatch. 


This was no game; it was his life. probably meant he was in for a really bad night, because hispelvis had gotten pretty quiet over the last two months. Gathering up the little courage he had left, trying desperately to summon exactly the right note of sharp and yet almost casual irritability, he said: "And you might as well stop that.
I may not know whats going to happen to Misery, but I know whats going to happen to me. He heard her rummaging around in the kitchen, throwing things, cursing in her strange Annie Wilkes language. Something seemed not at all right.   This was shortly, after he had asked the traditional when-the-sleeper-wakes question and she had told him he was in the little town of Sidewinder, Colorado. He had the tumbler twice, but both times the bobby-pin slipped off and the tumbler snapped back before he could do more than begin to move it.
